tubs.name: tubs

revisions.description: Added ibrpibtomib for automatic PIB to MIB conversion via 'smidump -f smiv2'.
Added ibrpib for all PIBs that are temporarily assigned to the ibr tree until they get official assignments from IANA. Fixed CONTACT-INFO to contain the current address.
Changed the module name from TUBS-REGISTRATION to TUBS-SMI.

ibr.name: ibr
ibr.description: The subtree delegated to the Department of Operating Systems and Computer Networks (Institut fuer Betriebssysteme und Rechnerverbund).

ibrpib.name: ibrpib
ibrpib.description: Only for PIBs that are temporarily assigned to the ibr tree until they get official assignments from IANA.

ibrpibtomib.name: ibrpibtomib
ibrpibtomib.description: Only for PIBs that are automatically converted to MIBs via 'smidump -f smiv2'.

ibrmibtopib.name: ibrmibtopib
ibrmibtopib.description: Only for MIBs that are automatically converted to PIBs via 'smidump -f sppi'.

IBRUnsigned64.name: IBRUnsigned64
IBRUnsigned64.description: A dummy type for automatic PIB to MIB conversion.

IBRInteger64.name: IBRInteger64
IBRInteger64.description: A dummy type for automatic PIB to MIB conversion.
